{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-42","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 42","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Tekst naslovnika se koristi da pruži korisnicima smernice o kakvoj vrsti informacija koje treba uneti u polje za unos.</p>\n<p>Ovo je primer elementa <code>input</code> sa zamjennikom postavljenim na <code>e.g. Jane Doe</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"e.g. Jane Doe\">\n</code></pre>\n<p>Dodajte tekst zamene <code>cat photo URL</code> u vaše polje <code>input</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804d9","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-42"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\">\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[36,38],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Izbrisali ste svoj element <code>input</code> ili ima neispravna sintaksa. Sve vrednosti atributa polja moraju biti obavijene navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('input').length);"},{"text":"<p><code>form</code> Vaše bi trebalo da ima samo element od <code>input</code>. Izbrišite druge elemente od HTML ili tekst unutar elemenata <code>form</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(\n  document.querySelector('form')?.children?.length === 1 &&\n    document.querySelector('form')?.innerText?.trim()?.length === 0\n);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>input</code> nema atribut <code>placeholder</code>. Osigurajte da postoji razmak nakon imena otvarajućeg taga i/ili da postoji razmak pre svih atributnih imena elementa.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('input')?.hasAttribute('placeholder'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>input</code> treba da ima atribut <code>placeholder</code> sa vrednošću <code>cat photo URL</code>. Vrednost je izostavljena ili postoje greške u kucanju. Zapamtite da vrednosti atributa elemenata moraju biti obavijene navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert(\n  document.querySelector('input')\n    ?.getAttribute('placeholder')\n    .replace(/\\s+/g, ' ')\n    .match(/^cat photo URL$/i)\n);"},{"text":"<p>Iako ste postavili atribut <code>input</code> elementa <code>placeholder</code> kao <code>cat photo URL</code>, savetuje se uvek da izbacujete vrednost atributa elementa i navodnike.</p>","testString":"assert(!/\\<\\s*input\\s+placeholder\\s*=\\s*cat\\s+photo\\s+url/i.test(code));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-42","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-43","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-41","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804d9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-42"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}